<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.156181>
    dc:description "FIGURES 8 – 15. 8, Myrsidea kathleenae male genital sac sclerite. 9, M. warwicki female metanotal margin and dorsoventral abdomen. 10 – 14, Male genital sac sclerite. 10, M. plumosi. 11, M. adamsae. 12, M. ochracei. 13, M. borbonici. 14, M. johnsoni. 15, M. palmai male metanotal margin and dorsoventral abdomen." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/156181/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.156180>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. 1 – 5, Myrsidea pycnonoti. 1, Dorsoventral male. 2, Ventral male terminalia. 3, Female metanotal margin and dorsoventral abdomen. 4, Male genitalia. 5, Male genital sac sclerite. 6, M. phillipsi male genital sac sclerite. 7, M. gieferi male ventral terminalia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/156180/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

